\(
ewcommand{\pp}{\partial} 
ewcommand{\sgn}{\mathrm{sgn}} 
ewcommand{\mdef}{\overset{\mathrm{def}}{=}}\) Definition of Classical Possion Bracket: $$[f, g]=\sum_{i=1, 2,\ldots, n} rac{\pp(f, g)}{\pp(p_i, q_i)}=\sum_{i=1, 2,\ldots, n}\left( rac{\pp f}{\pp p_i} rac{\pp g}{\pp q_i}- rac{\pp f}{\pp q_i} rac{\pp g}{\pp p_i}ight)$$ If we define \(p_{-i}\mdef q_{i}\) , and \(I=\{\pm 1, \pm, 2,\ldots, \pm n\}\) , we can rewrite it: $$[f, g]=\sum_{i\in I} \sgn(i)  rac{\pp f}{\pp p_i} rac{\pp g}{\pp p_{-i}}$$ Jacobi Identity is \([f,[g,h]]+[g,[h,f]]+[h,[f,g]]=0\) . With the new notation, we can rewrite it as $$ egin{aligned} \sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}[f,[g,h]] &=\sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}\sum_{i\in I}\sgn(i) rac{\pp f}{\pp p_i} rac{\pp}{\pp p_{-i}}\left(\sum_{j\in I}\sgn(j) rac{\pp g}{\pp p_j} rac{\pp h}{\pp p_{-j}}ight)\ &=\sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}\sum_{i, j\in I}\sgn(ij)\left( rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{-j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{j}}} + rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp g}{{\pp p_{j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2h}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{-j}}}ight)\ &=\sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}\sum_{i, j\in I}\sgn(ij)\left( rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{-j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{j}}} + rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{-j}}}ight)\ &=\sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}\sum_{i, j\in I}\sgn(ij)\left( rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{-j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{j}}} + rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{-j}}}ight)\ &=\sum_{\overrightarrow{fgh}}\sum_{i, j\in I}\sgn(ij)\left( rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{-j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{j}}} - rac{\pp f}{{\pp p_{i}}} rac{\pp h}{{\pp p_{-j}}} rac{\pp&#94;2g}{{\pp p_{-i}}{\pp p_{j}}}ight)\ &=0\end{aligned}$$ if (!document.getElementById('mathjaxscript_pelican_#%@#$@#')) { var align = "center", indent = "0em", linebreak = "false"; if (false) { align = (screen.width < 768) ? "left" : align; indent = (screen.width < 768) ? "